---
// Newsletter CTA component - shown at the end of blog posts
---

<section class="newsletter-cta">
  <div class="newsletter-content">
    <h2>Iscriviti alla newsletter.</h2>
    <p>Ricevi aggiornamenti settimanali su articoli e pensieri dal mondo tech. Niente spam, puoi cancellarti quando vuoi.</p>

    <form class="newsletter-form" action="#" method="POST">
      <input
        type="email"
        name="email"
        placeholder="La tua email"
        required
        class="email-input"
      />
      <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Iscriviti</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .newsletter-cta {
    margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-3xl);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(25, 30, 40, 1) 0%, rgba(35, 40, 55, 1) 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 20px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .newsletter-cta::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -40%;
    right: -10%;
    width: 350px;
    height: 350px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(120, 90, 180, 0.2) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .newsletter-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .newsletter-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .newsletter-content > p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .newsletter-form {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .email-input {
    flex: 1;
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    background: rgba(15, 20, 28, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .email-input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--blue-bright);
  }

  .email-input::placeholder {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .submit-btn {
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-xl);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    background: var(--blue);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .submit-btn:hover {
    background: var(--blue-bright);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .newsletter-cta {
      padding: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .newsletter-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .newsletter-form {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .submit-btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
